import json, os

base = r'E:\Github\Machine-Learning-Projects\NLP'

nb = {"cells":[{"cell_type":"markdown","metadata":{},"source":["# TF-IDF vs Embeddings Benchmark\n","\n","**NLP Traditional Preprocessing Project - Feature Pipeline Comparison**"]},{"cell_type":"markdown","metadata":{},"source":["## Project Overview\n","\n","Compare **classic TF-IDF** features with **modern dense embeddings** (Word2Vec averaged, Sentence Transformers) for text classification. Measure accuracy, training time, and practicality."]},{"cell_type":"markdown","metadata":{},"source":["## Learning Objectives\n","\n","1. Understand TF-IDF (sparse, interpretable, fast).\n","2. Understand dense embeddings (semantic, fixed-dimension).\n","3. Compare classification quality and speed.\n","4. Learn when each approach is appropriate.\n","5. Build intuition about representation quality."]},{"cell_type":"markdown","metadata":{},"source":["## Problem Statement\n","\n","**Do modern embeddings outperform classic TF-IDF** on a standard text classification benchmark? Controlled comparison."]},{"cell_type":"markdown","metadata":{},"source":["## Why This Project Matters\n","\n","- TF-IDF is simple, fast, and often surprisingly strong.\n","- Embeddings capture semantic similarity but need more compute.\n","- Wrong feature choice wastes resources.\n","- Understanding trade-offs guides architecture decisions."]},{"cell_type":"markdown","metadata":{},"source":["## Dataset Overview\n","\n","AG News, 5K subset, 4 classes.\n","\n","## Dataset Source and License Notes\n","\n","Hugging Face `fancyzhx/ag_news`. Free. Auto-download."]},{"cell_type":"markdown","metadata":{},"source":["## Environment Setup"]},{"cell_type":"code","execution_count":None,"metadata":{},"outputs":[],"source":["import subprocess, sys, importlib\n","for pkg in [\"pandas\",\"numpy\",\"matplotlib\",\"seaborn\",\"scikit-learn\",\"gensim\",\"sentence-transformers\",\"datasets\"]:\n","    try: importlib.import_module(pkg.replace(\"-\",\"_\"))\n","    except ImportError: subprocess.check_call([sys.executable,\"-m\",\"pip\",\"install\",\"-q\",pkg])\n","print(\"Ready.\")"]},{"cell_type":"markdown","metadata":{},"source":["## Imports"]},{"cell_type":"code","execution_count":None,"metadata":{},"outputs":[],"source":["import numpy as np, pandas as pd, matplotlib.pyplot as plt, seaborn as sns\n","import re, time, warnings\n","from sklearn.feature_extraction.text import TfidfVectorizer\n","from sklearn.linear_model import LogisticRegression\n","from sklearn.naive_bayes import MultinomialNB\n","from sklearn.svm import LinearSVC\n","from sklearn.base import clone\n","from sklearn.metrics import (accuracy_score, precision_score, recall_score, f1_score,\n","    classification_report, confusion_matrix, ConfusionMatrixDisplay)\n","from sklearn.model_selection import train_test_split\n","from gensim.models import Word2Vec\n","from sentence_transformers import SentenceTransformer\n","from datasets import load_dataset\n","warnings.filterwarnings(\"ignore\"); sns.set_style(\"whitegrid\")\n","%matplotlib inline\n","print(\"Loaded.\")"]},{"cell_type":"markdown","metadata":{},"source":["## Configuration / Constants"]},{"cell_type":"code","execution_count":None,"metadata":{},"outputs":[],"source":["SEED=42; N_SAMPLES=5000; TEST_SIZE=0.2; MAX_FEATURES=10000\n","CLASS_NAMES=[\"World\",\"Sports\",\"Business\",\"Sci/Tech\"]\n","np.random.seed(SEED)"]},{"cell_type":"markdown","metadata":{},"source":["## Dataset Download or Loading"]},{"cell_type":"code","execution_count":None,"metadata":{},"outputs":[],"source":["ds=load_dataset(\"fancyzhx/ag_news\",split=\"train\")\n","df=ds.to_pandas().sample(n=N_SAMPLES,random_state=SEED).reset_index(drop=True)\n","print(f\"Shape:{df.shape}\"); df.head(3)"]},{"cell_type":"markdown","metadata":{},"source":["## Data Validation Checks"]},{"cell_type":"code","execution_count":None,"metadata":{},"outputs":[],"source":["df=df.drop_duplicates(subset=[\"text\"]).reset_index(drop=True)\n","assert df[\"label\"].isin([0,1,2,3]).all()\n","df[\"word_count\"]=df[\"text\"].str.split().apply(len)\n","print(\"Validation passed.\")"]},{"cell_type":"markdown","metadata":{},"source":["## Exploratory Data Analysis"]},{"cell_type":"code","execution_count":None,"metadata":{},"outputs":[],"source":["fig,axes=plt.subplots(1,2,figsize=(12,4))\n","axes[0].hist(df[\"word_count\"],bins=50,color=\"steelblue\",edgecolor=\"white\"); axes[0].set_title(\"Word Count\")\n","for l,n in enumerate(CLASS_NAMES): axes[1].hist(df[df[\"label\"]==l][\"word_count\"],bins=30,alpha=0.5,label=n)\n","axes[1].legend(); axes[1].set_title(\"Words by Class\")\n","plt.tight_layout(); plt.show()"]},{"cell_type":"markdown","metadata":{},"source":["## Target Analysis"]},{"cell_type":"code","execution_count":None,"metadata":{},"outputs":[],"source":["cc=df[\"label\"].value_counts().sort_index()\n","fig,ax=plt.subplots(figsize=(8,4))\n","ax.bar(CLASS_NAMES,cc.values,color=[\"#4C72B0\",\"#DD8452\",\"#55A868\",\"#C44E52\"])\n","ax.set_title(\"Class Distribution\")\n","plt.tight_layout(); plt.show()"]},{"cell_type":"markdown","metadata":{},"source":["## Train/Validation/Test Split Strategy"]},{"cell_type":"code","execution_count":None,"metadata":{},"outputs":[],"source":["X_train,X_test,y_train,y_test=train_test_split(df[\"text\"],df[\"label\"],test_size=TEST_SIZE,random_state=SEED,stratify=df[\"label\"])\n","print(f\"Train:{len(X_train)}|Test:{len(X_test)}\")"]},{"cell_type":"markdown","metadata":{},"source":["## Preprocessing Strategy - Feature Pipelines\n","\n","1. **TF-IDF** - sparse bag-of-words with IDF weighting.\n","2. **Word2Vec Average** - train Word2Vec, average token vectors per doc.\n","3. **Sentence Transformers** - pretrained dense embeddings."]},{"cell_type":"code","execution_count":None,"metadata":{},"outputs":[],"source":["def simple_tokenize(text):\n","    return re.findall(r\"\\b\\w+\\b\", text.lower())"]},{"cell_type":"markdown","metadata":{},"source":["## Feature Engineering - Pipeline 1: TF-IDF"]},{"cell_type":"code","execution_count":None,"metadata":{},"outputs":[],"source":["t0=time.time()\n","tfidf=TfidfVectorizer(max_features=MAX_FEATURES,ngram_range=(1,2))\n","X_tr_tfidf=tfidf.fit_transform(X_train); X_te_tfidf=tfidf.transform(X_test)\n","tfidf_time=time.time()-t0\n","print(f\"TF-IDF: {X_tr_tfidf.shape}, time={tfidf_time:.2f}s\")"]},{"cell_type":"markdown","metadata":{},"source":["### Pipeline 2: Word2Vec Average"]},{"cell_type":"code","execution_count":None,"metadata":{},"outputs":[],"source":["train_tokenized=[simple_tokenize(t) for t in X_train]\n","test_tokenized=[simple_tokenize(t) for t in X_test]\n","t0=time.time()\n","w2v_model=Word2Vec(sentences=train_tokenized,vector_size=100,window=5,min_count=2,workers=4,seed=SEED,epochs=10)\n","def doc2vec_avg(tokens,model,dim=100):\n","    vecs=[model.wv[t] for t in tokens if t in model.wv]\n","    return np.mean(vecs,axis=0) if vecs else np.zeros(dim)\n","X_tr_w2v=np.array([doc2vec_avg(t,w2v_model) for t in train_tokenized])\n","X_te_w2v=np.array([doc2vec_avg(t,w2v_model) for t in test_tokenized])\n","w2v_time=time.time()-t0\n","print(f\"Word2Vec: {X_tr_w2v.shape}, time={w2v_time:.2f}s\")"]},{"cell_type":"markdown","metadata":{},"source":["### Pipeline 3: Sentence Transformers"]},{"cell_type":"code","execution_count":None,"metadata":{},"outputs":[],"source":["t0=time.time()\n","st_model=SentenceTransformer(\"all-MiniLM-L6-v2\")\n","X_tr_st=st_model.encode(X_train.tolist(),show_progress_bar=True,batch_size=64)\n","X_te_st=st_model.encode(X_test.tolist(),show_progress_bar=True,batch_size=64)\n","st_time=time.time()-t0\n","print(f\"SentenceTransformer: {X_tr_st.shape}, time={st_time:.2f}s\")"]},{"cell_type":"markdown","metadata":{},"source":["## Baseline Model\n","\n","TF-IDF + MultinomialNB"]},{"cell_type":"code","execution_count":None,"metadata":{},"outputs":[],"source":["bl=MultinomialNB(); bl.fit(X_tr_tfidf,y_train); y_pb=bl.predict(X_te_tfidf)\n","bl_acc=accuracy_score(y_test,y_pb); bl_f1=f1_score(y_test,y_pb,average=\"weighted\")\n","print(f\"BASELINE: Acc={bl_acc:.4f}, F1={bl_f1:.4f}\")\n","print(classification_report(y_test,y_pb,target_names=CLASS_NAMES))"]},{"cell_type":"markdown","metadata":{},"source":["## Full Pipeline x Classifier Comparison"]},{"cell_type":"code","execution_count":None,"metadata":{},"outputs":[],"source":["pipelines={\"TF-IDF\":(X_tr_tfidf,X_te_tfidf,tfidf_time),\"Word2Vec Avg\":(X_tr_w2v,X_te_w2v,w2v_time),\"SentenceTransformer\":(X_tr_st,X_te_st,st_time)}\n","classifiers_dense={\"LogisticRegression\":LogisticRegression(max_iter=1000,random_state=SEED),\"LinearSVC\":LinearSVC(max_iter=2000,random_state=SEED)}\n","classifiers_all={\"MultinomialNB\":MultinomialNB(),**classifiers_dense}\n","results=[]\n","for pn,(Xtr,Xte,pt) in pipelines.items():\n","    clfs=classifiers_all if pn==\"TF-IDF\" else classifiers_dense\n","    for cn,clf in clfs.items():\n","        m=clone(clf); m.fit(Xtr,y_train); yp=m.predict(Xte)\n","        results.append({\"Pipeline\":pn,\"Classifier\":cn,\"Accuracy\":accuracy_score(y_test,yp),\"F1\":f1_score(y_test,yp,average=\"weighted\"),\"Embed Time(s)\":round(pt,2)})\n","results_df=pd.DataFrame(results)\n","print(results_df.sort_values(\"F1\",ascending=False).to_string(index=False))"]},{"cell_type":"code","execution_count":None,"metadata":{},"outputs":[],"source":["fig,axes=plt.subplots(1,2,figsize=(14,5))\n","for pn in pipelines:\n","    sub=results_df[results_df[\"Pipeline\"]==pn]\n","    axes[0].barh([f\"{pn}+{c}\" for c in sub[\"Classifier\"]],sub[\"F1\"])\n","axes[0].set_title(\"F1 Score\"); axes[0].set_xlim(0.7,1.0)\n","times=pd.DataFrame([{\"Pipeline\":k,\"Time\":v[2]} for k,v in pipelines.items()])\n","axes[1].bar(times[\"Pipeline\"],times[\"Time\"],color=[\"#4C72B0\",\"#DD8452\",\"#55A868\"])\n","axes[1].set_title(\"Embedding Time (s)\"); axes[1].set_ylabel(\"Seconds\")\n","plt.tight_layout(); plt.show()"]},{"cell_type":"markdown","metadata":{},"source":["## LazyPredict Benchmark\n","\n","> Not used for NLP / embeddings tasks per best practices."]},{"cell_type":"markdown","metadata":{},"source":["## FLAML AutoML\n","\n","> Not used for NLP / embeddings tasks per best practices."]},{"cell_type":"markdown","metadata":{},"source":["## Additional - Sentence Transformers Deep Dive"]},{"cell_type":"code","execution_count":None,"metadata":{},"outputs":[],"source":["from sklearn.metrics.pairwise import cosine_similarity\n","pairs=[(\"Stock market rises\",\"Shares go up today\"),(\"Stock market rises\",\"Football match tonight\"),(\"Python programming\",\"Machine learning code\")]\n","for a,b in pairs:\n","    ea=st_model.encode([a]); eb=st_model.encode([b])\n","    sim=cosine_similarity(ea,eb)[0][0]\n","    print(f\"  '{a}' vs '{b}' -> similarity={sim:.4f}\")"]},{"cell_type":"markdown","metadata":{},"source":["## Top 3 Model Selection"]},{"cell_type":"code","execution_count":None,"metadata":{},"outputs":[],"source":["top3=results_df.sort_values(\"F1\",ascending=False).head(3).reset_index(drop=True)\n","print(top3[[\"Pipeline\",\"Classifier\",\"Accuracy\",\"F1\",\"Embed Time(s)\"]].to_string(index=False))\n","print(f\"Baseline F1={bl_f1:.4f}, Improvement: {((top3.iloc[0]['F1']-bl_f1)/bl_f1)*100:+.2f}%\")"]},{"cell_type":"markdown","metadata":{},"source":["## Final Training and Evaluation of Top 3"]},{"cell_type":"code","execution_count":None,"metadata":{},"outputs":[],"source":["top3_preds={}\n","for i,row in top3.iterrows():\n","    Xtr,Xte,_=pipelines[row[\"Pipeline\"]]\n","    if row[\"Classifier\"]==\"MultinomialNB\": m=MultinomialNB()\n","    elif row[\"Classifier\"]==\"LogisticRegression\": m=LogisticRegression(max_iter=1000,random_state=SEED)\n","    else: m=LinearSVC(max_iter=2000,random_state=SEED)\n","    m.fit(Xtr,y_train); yp=m.predict(Xte)\n","    top3_preds[f\"{row['Pipeline']}+{row['Classifier']}\"]=yp\n","    print(f\"\\n{'='*60}\")\n","    print(f\"#{i+1}: {row['Pipeline']}+{row['Classifier']}\")\n","    print(f\"{'='*60}\")\n","    print(classification_report(y_test,yp,target_names=CLASS_NAMES))"]},{"cell_type":"code","execution_count":None,"metadata":{},"outputs":[],"source":["fig,axes=plt.subplots(1,3,figsize=(18,5))\n","for idx,(n,yp) in enumerate(top3_preds.items()):\n","    ConfusionMatrixDisplay(confusion_matrix(y_test,yp),display_labels=CLASS_NAMES).plot(ax=axes[idx],cmap=\"Blues\",values_format=\"d\")\n","    axes[idx].set_title(f\"#{idx+1}\",fontsize=9)\n","plt.tight_layout(); plt.show()"]},{"cell_type":"markdown","metadata":{},"source":["## Error Analysis"]},{"cell_type":"code","execution_count":None,"metadata":{},"outputs":[],"source":["bp=list(top3_preds.values())[0]; em=bp!=y_test.values\n","edf=pd.DataFrame({\"text\":X_test.values[em],\"true\":y_test.values[em],\"pred\":bp[em]})\n","edf[\"true_class\"]=edf[\"true\"].map(dict(enumerate(CLASS_NAMES)))\n","edf[\"pred_class\"]=edf[\"pred\"].map(dict(enumerate(CLASS_NAMES)))\n","print(f\"Errors: {len(edf)}/{len(y_test)} ({len(edf)/len(y_test)*100:.1f}%)\")"]},{"cell_type":"markdown","metadata":{},"source":["## Interpretation and Business Insight\n","\n","1. TF-IDF is surprisingly competitive for topic classification.\n","2. Sentence Transformers capture semantics but need GPU for speed.\n","3. Word2Vec average loses document-level context.\n","4. TF-IDF is the fastest and most interpretable.\n","5. Embeddings shine on semantic similarity tasks."]},{"cell_type":"markdown","metadata":{},"source":["## Limitations\n","\n","Single dataset. Small subset. No fine-tuning. No GPU timing."]},{"cell_type":"markdown","metadata":{},"source":["## How to Improve This Project\n","\n","1. Fine-tune Sentence Transformers.\n","2. Test on semantic similarity tasks.\n","3. Add GloVe/FastText.\n","4. Larger dataset.\n","5. GPU benchmarking."]},{"cell_type":"markdown","metadata":{},"source":["## Production Considerations\n","\n","- TF-IDF: no model download, fast, interpretable.\n","- Embeddings: need model hosting, batch processing.\n","- Hybrid approaches can combine both."]},{"cell_type":"markdown","metadata":{},"source":["## Common Mistakes\n","\n","1. Using embeddings when TF-IDF suffices.\n","2. Not averaging Word2Vec properly.\n","3. Ignoring compute costs.\n","4. Not normalizing embeddings.\n","5. Assuming embeddings always win."]},{"cell_type":"markdown","metadata":{},"source":["## Mini Challenge / Exercises\n","\n","1. Add GloVe embeddings.\n","2. Test on sentiment (IMDB).\n","3. Hybrid TF-IDF + embeddings.\n","4. Dimensionality reduction on TF-IDF."]},{"cell_type":"markdown","metadata":{},"source":["## Final Summary / Key Takeaways\n","\n","| Pipeline | Pros | Cons |\n","|----------|------|------|\n","| TF-IDF | Fast, interpretable, strong baseline | No semantics, sparse |\n","| Word2Vec Avg | Captures word meaning | Loses doc structure |\n","| Sentence Transformers | Best semantics | Slow, large models |\n","\n","1. Always start with TF-IDF baseline.\n","2. Embeddings for semantic tasks.\n","3. TF-IDF competitive for topic classification.\n","4. Consider compute budget.\n","5. Hybrid approaches possible."]}],"metadata":{"kernelspec":{"display_name":"Python 3","language":"python","name":"python3"},"language_info":{"name":"python","version":"3.11.0"}},"nbformat":4,"nbformat_minor":5}

